  "method": [
    "Put flour and grease on a baking pan, and preheat the oven to 175 C.",
    "Mix baking powder and flour.",
    "Mix cream butter and 1 cup of sugar until fluffy.",
    "Put eggs and vanilla extract in it and beat well.",
    "Gradually pour butter mixture to the flour mixture, mix well.",
    "Bake it for around 30 minutes.",
    "Mix condensed milk, and whole milk, and evaporated milk.",
    "Put on the cake.",
    "Mix whipping cream, remaining sugar, and remaining vanilla until it",
    "is thick. Pour on the cake.",
